    • HybridAd

      public HybridAd​(android.content.Context context, java.lang.String adUnitId)
      Class constructor for a HybridAd model used to load a Hybrid ad and respond to ad lifecycle events. This ad can be used to load ad units of different types when placement could support a variety of different display methods
      Parameters:
      context - application context
      adUnitId - a valid ad unit ID
